sentence.text: To test whether this gene can confer a wide variety of psychiatric disorders, we carried out a case-control association analysis of three tagging single-nucleotide polymorphisms (rs2074896, rs2074897, and rs2074898) in the mitochondrial respiratory chain complex I assembly gene by sequencing 330 Han Chinese patients with schizophrenia and 330 well-matched healthy controls.
